gomodel:SYNGO_4931  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Immunogold-electronmicroscopy shows goldparticles in the synaptic cleft (Fig. 2Q-V) as well as in dendritic spines (ticket #4930).. Experimental description: \"Postembedding procedure was performed according to ... In brief, normal Wistar rats were perfused...\" (p.1033)\n\nM&M:\n\"The immunoreactions consisted of sequential incubations with a rabbit anti - MMP-9 antibody (Torrey Pines Biolabs, Inc.) diluted at 1:50, followed by species-specifi c goat secondary antibodies coupled to 10-nm gold particles (GE Healthcare)\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
